eTargeting.model
Class ListsModel

java.lang.Object
  eTargeting.model.ListsModel

public class ListsModel
extends java.lang.Object

The ListsModel class represents a list containing one or several subscribers and allows the user to create new lists.

A list is represented by the following information:

  • A unique ID.
  • A name.
  • A list of subscribers comma-separated.
  • The ID of the list's owner.
  • The current page number
